data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bath doublewide home located in Mt. Vernon offers a serene and peaceful country setting. The property is situated on 3.01 level acres, fully fenced, and boasts two outbuildings. The home has been well-maintained and features a new roof. Additionally, an inground storm shelter provides peace of mind during inclement weather. Whether you're seeking a quiet retreat or a place to start your own small farm, this property offers endless possibilities. Enjoy the tranquility of country living while still being within close proximity to all the amenities that Mt. Vernon has to offer. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own!
